# WillyBeat Preset v2
version: 2
name:    UK Drill Rim Pattern
genres:  Hip-Hop, UK Drill, Drill, Rap, Urban, 2020s, UK, London, Sliding 808s, Aggressive, Club, Mid-tempo, Sample-based, Drum Machine, Bouncy
type:    Regular
